OL,3,CFive arrested after shooting in Swindon
OL,5,FFive people have been arrested
OL,6,Ffollowing a shooting in Gorse Hill,
OL,7,FSwindon, which took place on Friday
OL,8,F19th July.
OL,10,FOfficers responded to reports of a
OL,11,Fgunshot being fired in St Paul's
OL,12,FStreet, Gorse Hill just before 9pm.
OL,14,FA man in his 30s was been taken to
OL,15,Fhospital with a suspected gunshot
OL,16,Fwound.
OL,18,FWiltshire police have describe his
OL,19,Fcondition as "serious but stable".
OL,21,FPolice have arrested five people:
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/2
