OL,3,CFive arrested after shooting in Swindon
OL,5,FCurrently they all remain in custody
OL,6,Ffor questioning.
OL,8,FA cordon is in place on St Paul's
OL,9,FStreet and Queens Drive while officers
OL,10,Fcarry out their investigations.
OL,12,FPolice are urging anyone with
OL,13,Finformation to contact them.
